I have no problem with him doing design work for games, and to be quite honest, as slow as he is doing sequential art, it might be a better fit for him. The thing that pisses me off is he just drops BC like it's nothing. I could deal with waiting, but to make you wait and then just put it on hold indefinitely...<br>
<br>
He said something about waiting until he can devote all his time to the comic... He said the EXACT same thing between that huge delay between 6 and 7. It didn't seem to help him then, so why should we believe him now?<br>
<br>
I still like his art, I still like the comic (and I'm sure I'll still buy it if it ever comes out), but this pisses me the hell off. <p><table width=100% border=0>
